Not sure why but I enjoy the second disk more. From the story were he has to skip swim class to were he helps his little sister and her hair bow problem. He also helps Yukari when she is uncertian about things. All the stories are nice light hearted fun. Remeber this is a english subbed series but do not let that turn you away. I was not sure when I got the first this one but I have enjoyed the first two disks and look forward to the third one.
